ork, making work assignments, and they discuss every week","box":[[75,510],[1203,515],[1203,545],[74,540]]},{"text":"x the plan","box":[[1188,518],[1360,520],[1360,544],[1188,542]]},{"text":"for","box":[[1349,518],[1422,522],[1421,544],[1348,541]]},{"text":"production and the problems.","box":[[74,549],[588,547],[588,574],[75,576]]},{"text":"This person is usually experienced in work.","box":[[598,547],[1353,552],[1353,580],[598,575]]},{"text":"The quality yuan is","box":[[74,584],[411,583],[411,610],[75,611]]},{"text":"salsoanexperiencedworker.","box":[[397,584],[903,586],[903,611],[397,609]]},{"text":"He inspects the painting","box":[[931,586],[1353,588],[1353,615],[931,613]]},{"text":"job of each worker, and if there is a problem he will bring it up with the","box":[[73,617],[1371,620],[1371,651],[73,647]]},{"text":"worker, or raise the","box":[[74,657],[426,656],[426,680],[75,681]]},{"text":"e problem at a meeting if it persists.","box":[[412,655],[1073,657],[1073,684],[412,682]]},{"text":"There are also inspection specialists who are technicians, from","box":[[176,689],[1290,693],[1289,720],[176,716]]},{"text":"1the","box":[[1278,696],[1351,696],[1351,718],[1278,718]]},{"text":"section.","box":[[74,728],[214,726],[215,750],[75,752]]},{"text":"Sometimes these are experienced workers who have been ","box":[[244,725],[1203,728],[1203,755],[244,752]]},{"text":"given","box":[[1194,730],[1283,730],[1283,754],[1194,754]]},{"text":"promotions.","box":[[73,762],[286,760],[286,787],[74,789]]},{"text":"They work in the office and come down to inspect.","box":[[299,760],[1162,761],[1162,789],[299,788]]},{"text":"They are","box":[[1196,765],[1335,765],[1335,789],[1196,789]]},{"text":"non-production staff, and work in offices.","box":[[73,795],[813,794],[813,824],[73,825]]},{"text":"The come at non-fixed prriods","box":[[847,799],[1351,799],[1351,823],[847,823]]},{"text":"as uninvited guests, and have the power to reject work ard make you do it","box":[[74,830],[1354,833],[1